{"tid":1924750,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"如果所有聯賽都腰斬 其實一定會有冠軍同有降班","createTime":"2020-03-14T01:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T11:44:06.000Z","uid":128321,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a7bf7940723b5190d4efcc4910da0f2d2be3c696","tid":1924750,"uid":128321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T01:05:50.000Z","msg":"我客觀講<br />\n因為理論上如果有腰斬而無冠亦無人降班<br />\n即係個聯賽排名已經唔valid<br />\n佢唔可以同時無冠又降班<br />\n但又用個個排名去訂邊一隊打下屆歐洲賽<br />\n即係話變相今年聯賽會懸空<br />\n下屆歐洲賽要用一個新方法去訂邊隊有份打<br />\n<br />\n但相反如果佢要用番個排名去訂下屆歐洲賽<br />\n即係默認左今年聯賽係有效<br />\n即使聯賽腰斬左<br />\n個最終排名都係一個有效排名<br />\n即使有球隊踢左唔同場次<br />\n領先一分或者10分都好<br />\n都要用個個排名去訂冠軍同邊隊降班<br />\n<br />\n純粹理性分析下<br />\n始終都係人命最緊要<br />\n<br />\n再加上我估計有好多商業因素係裡面<br />\n你陽太多人比左錢贊助左d比賽同球隊<br />\n所以即使腰斬左但唔計最終排名嘅機會可能好細"},{"pid":"e95ad6ca7ee354872f8d5c557b0d303480133fa6","tid":1924750,"uid":46151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T01:18:13.000Z","msg":"一句到尾好簡單<br />\n只要冇球隊因而損失就唔會有人嘈<br />\n所以一定係唔降班只升班<br />\n<br />\n唯一要再諗嘅就係歐洲賽席位<br />\n要睇返聯賽球隊自己嘅決定<br />\n可能係用現有排名<br />\n亦都可能係踢附加賽"},{"pid":"d733823cf797ae280bc68c54e9bbdc3f434ccc4f","tid":1924750,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T01:18:23.000Z","msg":"點安排都會有人不滿<br />\n<br />\n英冠3隊照升班<br />\n英超取消降班<br />\n<br />\n下年英超23隊<br />\n一年踢44場<br />\n<br />\n排名上唔知點處理<br />\n點安排都會有人不滿<br />\n特別歐聯區 6，7隊係數字上有機"},{"pid":"ee4dd2959820750ac9706a6991e4ae4aacc9727d","tid":1924750,"uid":191926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d733823cf797ae280bc68c54e9bbdc3f434ccc4f","tid":1924750,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T01:18:23.000Z","msg":"點安排都會有人不滿<br />\n<br />\n英冠3隊照升班<br />\n英超取消降班<br />\n<br />\n下年英超23隊<br />\n一年踢44場<br />\n<br />\n排名上唔知點處理<br />\n點安排都會有人不滿<br />\n特別歐聯區 6，7隊係數字上有機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T01:22:39.000Z","msg":"如果時間無法安排<br />\n取消出年足總盃 聯賽盃<br />\n<br />\n大量加開週中比賽<br />\n出年降班要降6隊"},{"pid":"0ac7fb568ad9baf5ab62f1bf45f2912cfaef8716","tid":1924750,"uid":134421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T01:29:43.000Z","msg":"點安排都有人不滿<br />\n但降班同冠軍利益最大<br />\n所以照頒冠同唔降班就少左好多隊嘈<br />\n淨返就係歐冠最難搞"},{"pid":"f2b4a0482262d5d89033d3e959962652633183c0","tid":1924750,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T01:30:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.foxsports.com.au/football/liverpool-to-be-awarded-premier-league-with-plan-that-could-see-no-teams-relegated-for-next-season-report/news-story/04ec1185a7abc3e80ba00301a70f7c85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxsports.com.au%2Ffootball%2Fliverpool-to-be-awarded-premier-league-with-plan-that-could-see-no-teams-relegated-for-next-season-report%2Fnews-story%2F04ec1185a7abc3e80ba00301a70f7c85&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=5a0e28b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxsports.com.au/football/liverpool-to-be-awarded-premier-league-with-plan-that-could-see-no-teams-relegated-for-next-season-report/news-story/04ec1185a7abc3e80ba00301a70f7c85</a><br />\n<br />\n比24隊先會大家happy"},{"pid":"036eeb6c8695f002ef44d0209bdfe0487c06f4e9","tid":1924750,"uid":128321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2b4a0482262d5d89033d3e959962652633183c0","tid":1924750,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T01:30:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.foxsports.com.au/football/liverpool-to-be-awarded-premier-league-with-plan-that-could-see-no-teams-relegated-for-next-season-report/news-story/04ec1185a7abc3e80ba00301a70f7c85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxsports.com.au%2Ffootball%2Fliverpool-to-be-awarded-premier-league-with-plan-that-could-see-no-teams-relegated-for-next-season-report%2Fnews-story%2F04ec1185a7abc3e80ba00301a70f7c85&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=5a0e28b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxsports.com.au/f